{"tid":1100164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以掃黃為名整治互聯網","createTime":"2019-04-10T08:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:22:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68b562d09e7ba967181a9917b09111bfae9ef1f7","tid":1100164,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190410/20652731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F20652731&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=ad5448e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F20652731&h=6f154a05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190410/20652731</a><br />\n<br />\n以掃黃為名整治互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190410/large/10ce8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190410%2Flarge%2F10ce8p.jpg&h=7e1a83f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n截至今年2月，內地網民達8.29億；圖為內地一間網吧。<br />\n<br />\n新浪封殺處罰「發佈時政有害訊息」的微博同時，全國「掃黃打非」辦公室昨日通報，為嚴厲打擊「傳播低俗訊息」行為，營造風清氣正的網絡文化環境，即日起在全國範圍內開展為期八個月的「網上低俗訊息專項整治」，顯示中共此波對互聯網的整治是一場全國性的統一行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三學者論政 遭秋後算賬<br />\n<br />\n嚴打低俗網遊<br />\n<br />\n據介紹，此次專項行動於4月啟動，將持續開展八個月，綜合運用行政管理、行業規範、道德約束等多種手段，重點清理網絡傳播淫穢色情和夾雜淫穢色情訊息內容；以性為賣點不適合傳播的內容；宣揚違背正確婚戀觀和家庭倫理道德的內容；網絡惡搞、調侃等迎合低級趣味的內容；宣揚暴力、血腥、恐怖、殘酷的內容等。<br />\n<br />\n全國「掃黃打非辦」要求各地組織協調網信、工信、公安、文化和市場監管、廣播電視等部門，重點排查網絡文學、直播、短視頻、網絡遊戲、微博、微信等平台，對內容格調低俗的要及時下架下線，對價值導向出現偏差，含法律法規禁止內容的予以查處；嚴打利用低俗獵奇內容等手段吸引流量的直播；嚴打「擦邊球」為噱頭、以低俗手段營銷的網遊。有關負責人指，此次專項行動堅持網上網下統籌管理，統一標準、統一尺度。網絡企業要自查自糾，於專項行動開始30日內對存量內容全面清查，同時希望公眾積極參與，舉報違法違規行為。<br />\n<br />\n新華社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n三學者論政 遭秋後算賬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n林培瑞接力聯署 促清華准許章潤復職<br />\n<br />\n三學者論政 遭秋後算賬<br />\n網絡清洗升級 指發佈「時政有害訊息」中共文字獄 50名人微博被封"},{"pid":"d1ac7863aef08a07035356922cb87b3d49bd8a66","tid":1100164,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"打個飛機都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d6bf6055844f4b9e0a3f64c666f755f5ab8b73","tid":1100164,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1ac7863aef08a07035356922cb87b3d49bd8a66","tid":1100164,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"打個飛機都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"lm等睇成為強姦大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻小學雞治國真係國難<br />\n生肯率已經低<br />\nd人唔扑嘢遲d就立法強制授精"},{"pid":"85f6b5c6d8d74e3e1d09bd6886f6c886d1831c44","tid":1100164,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1ac7863aef08a07035356922cb87b3d49bd8a66","tid":1100164,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"打個飛機都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"你可以對住習大大打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2001971/org/47a873f54a631d7b31e88b271a08b9d8.JPG/9EmhA0JLH-e73wcAYrUDioyr6VbVhSiUfN173Hzde9w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2001971%2Forg%2F47a873f54a631d7b31e88b271a08b9d8.JPG%2F9EmhA0JLH-e73wcAYrUDioyr6VbVhSiUfN173Hzde9w%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=741a44d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e922f9dcb34ec2fd253a5a4a6e637e3da419b087","tid":1100164,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f6b5c6d8d74e3e1d09bd6886f6c886d1831c44","tid":1100164,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1ac7863aef08a07035356922cb87b3d49bd8a66","tid":1100164,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco